mit eine verlässliche Grundlage für ein erfolgreiches Studium der Volkswirtschaftslehre. Band I: Modul 1.1: Einführung in die VolkswirtschaftslehreModul 1.2: Mikroökonomie und WettbewerbspolitikBand II: Modul 2.1: MakroökonomieModul 2.2: Geld und WährungBand III: Modul 3.1: Wirtschaftspolitik I: StabilisierungspolitikModul 3.2: Wirtschaftspolitik II: Finanz- und Sozialpolitik   aThe three volumes cover the essential themes of macroeconomics included in an undergraduate program of study. Each volume deals with one year of study or a single modular unit. The volumes build on each other thematically, but are designed to be used independently, so each volume can be read alone. The updated new edition has been expanded to include a chapter on prosperity indicators.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jun 2020) 0aMacroeconomics. 0aMoney. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / Macroeconomics.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2015z9783110438734oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831104527470 cprintz978311045268640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311045269340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110452693423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110452693.jpg  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2015  aZDB-23-DGGb2015